snippet.title: Aiming For the Top Action Game - Why It’s The Best? BlazBlue Entropy Effect:  EA Content Revealed
snippet.description:
BlazBlue Entropy Effect will be launched on Steam on 8/16/2023 at 10:00 AM (UTC+8). The price will be $20 USD, and there will be a discount for the first week. Add it to your Wishlist now for the latest Early Access updates and Discounts! 

Steam Store Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2273430/
Discord：https://discord.gg/2s8sQbmtpE
#blazblue #bbee
